<div class="container">
<div class="center">
  <h1 class="Vlt-title--icon Vlt-title--center">
      <svg class="Vlt-icon Vlt-icon--larger Vlt-blue-dark"><use xlink:href="/symbol/volta-icons.svg#Vlt-icon-group"/></svg>
      Nexmo Developer Relations Team
  </h1>

  <br>

  <p class="p-large">
    Our mission is to build a world-class open source documentation platform to help developers build connected products.
  </p>
  <p class="p-large">
    Here are some of the people behind Nexmo Developer. Oh, and we're hiring for <a href="#join">the developer relations team</a> and <a href="https://nexmo.bamboohr.co.uk/jobs/">other teams at Nexmo</a>.
  </p>

  <br>


  <div class="Vlt-grid">
    <% @team['current'].shuffle.each do |member| %>
      <%= render partial: 'profile', locals: member.symbolize_keys %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2><b>Alumni</b></h2>

  <div class="Vlt-grid">
    <% @team['alumni'].shuffle.each do |member| %>
      <%= render partial: 'profile', locals: member.symbolize_keys %>
    <% end %>
  </div>  

  <hr />

  <h2><b>Contributors</b></h2>

  <p>Many of the improvements made to Nexmo Developer have come from our wonderful community.</p>
  <p>Check out our <a href="https://github.com/Nexmo/nexmo-developer/graphs/contributors">Contributors</a> page on GitHub.</p>

  <hr>


  <div class="Vlt-grid">
    <div class="Vlt-col" style="text-align: right">
      <a href="/spotlight"><img src="/assets/images/developer_spotlight_logo.png" /></a>
    </div>
    <div class="Vlt-col Vlt-col--3of4">
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />
      <h2 id="write-for-nexmo"><b>Write for Nexmo</b></h2>
  You don't have to be part of the team to write for Nexmo. <br /> Thanks to our <a href="/spotlight">Developer Spotlight</a> program, you can get paid $400 to write for us.
      </div>
    </div>

  <hr />

  <h2 id="join"><b>Join the team</b></h2>

  <p>If what we are building sounds interesting to you please see our open positions and get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:devrel@nexmo.com">devrel@nexmo.com</a>.</p>

  <br>

  <% @careers.group_by(&:role_group).each do |group_name, careers| %>
    <h3><%= group_name %></h3>
    <div class="Vlt-grid Vlt-grid--margin-top1">
      <% careers.each do |career| %>
        <div class="Vlt-col Vlt-col--1of2">
          <div class="Vlt-card Vlt-card--center Nxd-career">
            <svg class="Vlt-icon Vlt-icon--larger Vlt-blue-dark"><use xlink:href="/symbol/volta-icons.svg#Vlt-icon-<%= career.icon == 'account' ? 'user' : career.icon == 'book' ? 'books' : career.icon %>"/></svg>
              <hr>
              <h2>
                <%= career.title %>
                <% unless career.published %>
                    [Hidden]
                <% end %>
                <small class="Nxd-career__subtitle"><%= career.location %></small>
              </h2>

            <div class="Nxd-career__content">
              <%= career.description_short.render_markdown %>
            </div>
            <%= link_to "Find out more", career, class: 'Vlt-btn Vlt-btn--secondary Vlt-btn--app' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
</div>
